# Node.js CI/CD Pipeline using Jenkins

## 🚀 Overview

This project demonstrates a complete CI/CD pipeline using Jenkins.

## ⚙️ Tools Used

* Jenkins
* Docker
* Node.js
* GitHub

## 🔁 Pipeline Stages

1. Source Stage (GitHub trigger)
2. Build Stage (npm install)
3. Test Stage (Jest + ESLint)
4. Security Scan (npm audit)
5. Containerization (Docker build & push)
6. Deploy Stage (Docker container)
7. Notification Stage

## 🐳 Run Locally

```
npm install
npm start
```

## 🧪 Run Tests

```
npm test
```

## 🌐 Access App

http://localhost:3000
